‚ćĚ   64=Horizontal scroll bar (must also set limit) [Not in Dyalog]
‚ćĚ   128=Hide (the) scroll bar if not needed [Always auto-hidden in Dyalog]
‚ćĚ   256=Disable extended selection (only ‚ąä 1; can't use shift-click selection)

